steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi006sub" and Comment "Testing Sub"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi006sub" display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi006" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi006" display
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi006subs" from list
When I edit API method "DELETE" with endpoint "/api/jitapi006subs/:id"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - DefinitionValue Table "2" - row "1" - value "",""
When I click tab "Response params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi006sub"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "5" - value "jitapi006_id","Column Definition","jitapi006_id"
When I close the floating panel
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
When I drag the table Name "jitapi006sub" to new location with x: "200", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jitapi006" to table Name "jitapi006sub"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see the realtion path display
When I sleep 2
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi006subs" from list
When I wait query data API "jitapi006subs.jitapi006_id" is fetched completely
